          </div>
        </div>
      </a>



      <a href="/blog/2016/9/7/persuasion-2-your-writers-persona-1-1" class="BlogItem-pagination-link BlogItem-pagination-link--next">
        <div class="BlogItem-pagination-link-content">
          <div class="BlogItem-pagination-link-label">Next</div>
          <h4 class="BlogItem-pagination-link-title">Persuasion (2): Your writer's persona</h4>
